# Example npm configuration. Copy to .npmrc and adjust for your environment.
# .npmrc itself is gitignored to keep personal mirrors/auth out of the repo.
#
# China mainland users: uncomment the mirror lines below for faster downloads.
# Other regions: leave them commented to use the default registry.npmjs.org.

# registry=https://registry.npmjs.org/
# electron_mirror=https://npmmirror.com/mirrors/electron/
# electron_builder_binaries_mirror=https://npmmirror.com/mirrors/electron-builder-binaries/
